    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_2ad2cdc7">
            <lb />Valkyries thunder through the storm
            <lb />-
            <seg ana="#phantom_body" resp="#np" type="topic slogan">
                when Phantom Fingers play
            </seg>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_81452811">
            <lb />These are the Phantom
            <lb />Hands of a thousand
            <lb />immortal pianists; their
            <lb />glorious
            genius preserv-
            <lb />ed forever, through the
            <lb />miracle of
            <name type="brand">
                Welte-
                <lb />Mignon*
            </name>
            reproduction.
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_9280ed63">
            <lb />Who but a
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/119466821">Samaroff</persName> can achieve
            <lb />the crashing fortissimo with
            <lb />which <persName type="composer">Wagner</persName>
            meant his glorious
            <lb />composition to be played? Or,
            <seg ana="#suit_every_mood" resp="#np" type="topic">
                as
                <lb />your mood changes
            </seg>, who but
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/116014490">de<lb />Pachmann</persName>
            can so entrance you
            <lb />with <persName type="composer">Chopin's</persName> sensuous Nocturne?
            <lb />True music-lovers are satisfied only
            <lb />with the world's greatest masters.
            <lb />The <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon*</name> satisfies in this
            <lb />respect as well as in the
            <seg ana="#exact_reproduction">
                uncanny
                <lb />fidelity
            </seg> with which it reproduces
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_67364924">
            <lb />the renditions of the scores of
            <lb />master musicians who have played
            <lb />upon it.
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#invisibility" resp="#np" type="topic">
                The <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon*</name> is invisible
            </seg>
            <lb />and does not interfere with manual
            <lb />playing. It is obtainable in practi-
            <lb />cally every good make of piano,
            <lb />both grand and upright. Write
            <lb />for interesting brochure. <orgName>Auto-
            <lb />Pneumatic Action</orgName> Co.,
            <persName>
                W. C.
                <lb />Heaton, President
            </persName>, <address>12th Ave., at
            <lb />51st St., New York.</address>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_629a134c">
            <lb /><name type="brand">Welte-Mignon<lb />(Licensee)</name>
            <lb />Hear it-in comparison. There's a nearby dealer
            <lb />*Licensed under the original <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon</name> patents.
        </div>
